{
  "stem": "9878.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had Ukrainians in Germany that they are going to make a [NON-ENGLISH], a independent Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So now, the Germans promised them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They never kept the promise, but they promised them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So our biggest enemies and our biggest-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] what do you call it-- [? destructions ?] of our people by the population living in-- around-- in our area.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not as much as the Poles, because the Poles were there, strangers themselves.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Even so, it was Poland because this was Ukrainian land.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was [NON-ENGLISH] Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After the First World War, they allotted it to Poland, but the Ukrainians were the majority.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were the majority.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they, they, they, they-- at first, they started right away when the Germans came in, but not as systematically kill-- start killing.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This family was-- this father was killed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This son was killed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This woman went--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For example, they gave out all kind of orders.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A Jew is supposed to have a, a, a armband with a Star of David on his arm.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This wasn't enough.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then they put a, a disk, a yellow disk, about 4 inches wide, yellow like this yellow, and, and a disk on the back, on the shoulder.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Why the disk and this together?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know, because other places, they had only a disk on them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they were so brutalizing the population in order to put a fear in the-- in the people's minds they should never thought about resisting.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because for any resistance, any little resistance, they would-- they would kill you for, for, for just like this.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And naturally, if anybody were to arm-- for example, a, a, a Jewish kid, he was a friend of my who was about a year younger than me.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
